OAuth-Simple

Simple OAuth authorization on your site


INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc OAuth::Simple

You can also look for information at:

    Github
        https://github.com/Foxcool/OAuth-Simple

    Bugs & Issues
        https://github.com/Foxcool/OAuth-Simple/issues

    RT, CPAN's request tracker (report bugs here)
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=OAuth-Simple

    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/OAuth-Simple

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/OAuth-Simple

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/OAuth-Simple/


